        <h2>MyLettertoOrioles</h2>
        <p class="muted">An open note from a lifelong Maryland fan.</p>
      </header>

      <p>Dear Orioles,</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for the energy and the joy you bring to the city. The club means a lot to
        me and my family. I would love to see continued focus on player development, strong
        defense, and real fan access. Game days are better when the park feels like home.
      </p>

      <p>
        I am excited for the season ahead and I am ready to cheer. Let us make the next run
        one to remember.
      </p>

      <p>With respect,</p>
      <p>Mike Upman</p>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <section aria-labelledby="ps">
        <h3 id="ps">Notes</h3>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Keep building through the farm system.</li>
          <li>Lean into fan experience at the park.</li>
          <li>Celebrate the history and the future in equal measure.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </article>

